cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.HC, cs.SE, cs.DC

The paper discusses the use of cloud computing in the healthcare domain, which involves aspects of cybersecurity (cs.CR), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), software engineering (cs.SE), and distributed computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper focuses on the design and implementation of cloud-based eHealth frameworks (cs.CY).
